{"tid":155000,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"又多一單!! 警冚九龍城黑幫武器庫 拉一男子撿2把仿製槍","createTime":"2017-03-13T16:48:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-13T18:33:21.000Z","uid":60831,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"95e549fd17257abc1f5d95469ba6f3e1aacb0ef8","tid":155000,"uid":60831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T16:48:46.000Z","msg":"深水埗警區反三合會行動組人員與深水埗情報組探員，今日聯合進行代號「雷霆一七」( THUNDERBOLT 17)的反三合會行動，下午4時50分，突擊搜查九龍城城南道11至13號一單位，拘捕一名37歲<span style=\"color: red;\">南亞男子</span>，並撿獲兩枝鐵通、一把自製長刀、一把開山刀、兩枝仿製槍械及一個冰壺。<br />\n<br />\n被捕男子有黑幫背景，涉嫌藏有攻擊性武器、藏有仿製槍械及藏有工具可作吸食毒品用途，現正被扣留調查。警方表示，行動仍在進行中，不排除有更多人被捕。<br />\n<br />\n蝻亞人係香港除咗好事之外，真係咩都做齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今日蝻亞既犯罪新聞已經有四宗 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n張超雄好波 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b58a18b1e056fd80f5c8d516ae7273530b400041","tid":155000,"uid":30966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T16:49:23.000Z","msg":"我識既南亞人好nice"},{"pid":"867ffa1e0abb63b5407d4fede97b7f23fc164f7d","tid":155000,"uid":8776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T17:35:03.000Z","msg":"仿製槍係咪即係bb彈槍？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57ecbba3feae051ef35b78bda14b48687f7095e4","tid":155000,"uid":13149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T17:53:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仿製槍係咪即係bb彈槍？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n氣槍，改大焦耳可以打入肉"},{"pid":"e1149501cd3748622d2adebf3043329da5cdb664","tid":155000,"uid":58209,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T18:25:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>仿製槍係咪即係bb彈槍？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 